OL,3,CIndia swelters in record-breaking 50C
OL,4,Cheatwave
OL,6,FNorthern India is experiencing a
OL,7,Frecord-breaking heatwave, with
OL,8,Ftemperatures soaring above 50.5C in
OL,9,Fsome places.
OL,11,FDelhi recorded its highest ever
OL,12,Ftemperature of 49.9 degrees on
OL,13,FTuesday, surpassing a previous record
OL,14,Fof 49.2C in May 2022.
OL,16,FThe oppressive heat has forced
OL,17,Fauthorities in the capital to impose
OL,18,Fwater rationing, with some areas
OL,19,Fstruggling to access water, and others
OL,20,Fleft with none at all.
