OL,4,Cheatwave
OL,6,FElsewhere, the temperature in the city
OL,7,Fof Churu in the state of Rajasthan
OL,8,Fclimbed to 50.5C. Sirsa, a city in the
OL,9,Fstate of Haryana, saw thermometers
OL,10,Freach 50.3C, Indian authorities said.
OL,12,FThe country's weather department
OL,13,Fexpects temperatures to stay high
OL,14,Facross the region for the next few
OL,15,Fdays and has put several states on
OL,16,Fhigh alert.
OL,18,FIt said heatwave conditions will
OL,19,Fcontinue in Delhi on Wednesday but are
OL,20,Fexpected to subside starting Thursday.
